com.orm.androrm
Class FilterSet

java.lang.Object
  com.orm.androrm.FilterSet

public class FilterSet
extends Object

Filter Sets are a mechanism, to execute complex queries on the model classes in a very easy manner by using the field names in these classes.

Example:
If you for example want all Suppliers, that have a Branch which's name contains Pretoria the FilterSet would be the following. 

 FilterSet filter = new FilterSet();
 filter.contains("mBranches__mName", "Pretoria");

Author:
Philipp Giese
